# --- Highlightly Football API (server-side ONLY) ---
# Read by the serverless proxy in /api. NEVER exposed to the browser — do not
# prefix with VITE_ (that would inline it into the bundle). With no key, the app
# runs on its static seed snapshot and never advances on fabricated data.
#
# Get a key at https://highlightly.net/ (free Basic tier). The direct platform
# (https://soccer.highlightly.net) authenticates with the x-rapidapi-key header.
# Put the REAL key in .env.local (gitignored), not in this example file.

HIGHLIGHTLY_KEY=
WC_LEAGUE_ID=1635
WC_SEASON=2026
